data.description: Application of leadership, mentoring, and communication skills. Includes engagement in leadership experience to support STEM student success as well as activities to enhance participants' leadership development.

data.description: Provides current and potential peer leaders the opportunity to reflect on and think critically about their personal goals, identities, and experiences that inform their development as a peer leader. Increase awareness and develop practical skills to promote inclusion and success for students with diverse identities, and learn how to connect students with campus and community resources.
